AUDIO: 'be available over time. I reached out and&nbsp; asked them for comment and they said most&nbsp;&nbsp; likely early February. So we all get this&nbsp; for free, not just the research paper,&nbsp;&nbsp; but source code too! Thank you&nbsp; so much! What a time to be alive!'

